Package asgn2Containers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DangerousGoodsContainer
    A dangerous goods container is a special type of tank container for transporting flammable, explosive or toxic goods.
    FreightContainer
    This class is used to represent the characteristics of a generic freight, or intermodal, cargo container.
    GeneralGoodsContainer
    A general-purpose, or "dry", container is a freight container with no special characteristics.
    RefrigeratedContainer
    A refrigerated container is a special type of container for transporting perishable goods.
